            <div type="transcript" id="J831">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Dying! To be afraid of thee</l>
                    <l>One must to thine Artillery</l>
                    <l>Have left exposed a Friend --</l>
                    <l>Than thine old Arrow is a Shot</l>
                    <l>Delivered straighter to the Heart</l>
                    <l>The leaving Love behind.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Not for itself, the Dust is shy,</l>
                    <l>But, enemy, Beloved be</l>
                    <l>Thy Batteries divorce.</l>
                    <l>Fight sternly in a Dying eye</l>
                    <l>Two Armies, Love and Certainty</l>
                    <l>And Love and the Reverse.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
